  "detailed_description": "A kingdom fallen, a prince exiled.<br><br>Restore her glory, his journey begins. <br><br>Features:<br><br><strong>Exploration</strong><br>Explore a big and interconnected world, gaining new abilities to take on new areas!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/98515804b222b6cdc5da3765c7a8c033.poster.avif?t=1576745789\" width=626 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/98515804b222b6cdc5da3765c7a8c033.webm?t=1576745789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/98515804b222b6cdc5da3765c7a8c033.mp4?t=1576745789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Combat</strong><br>Mix of Top-down shooter and Hack-and-slash combat, with multiple skills for different enemies. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/9d4f3157c1bbc06787c364d4c2aa63af.poster.avif?t=1576745789\" width=626 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/9d4f3157c1bbc06787c364d4c2aa63af.webm?t=1576745789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/9d4f3157c1bbc06787c364d4c2aa63af.mp4?t=1576745789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Air Combat</strong><br>Jump into your airship to explore and fight in the air. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/3ed61f40b6a3f38d7a3e02f35f903180.poster.avif?t=1576745789\" width=626 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/3ed61f40b6a3f38d7a3e02f35f903180.webm?t=1576745789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/3ed61f40b6a3f38d7a3e02f35f903180.mp4?t=1576745789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Platforming</strong><br>Use combat abilities to traverse the terrain. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/0fee023fc7644584482aa01d1bbff8b8.poster.avif?t=1576745789\" width=626 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/0fee023fc7644584482aa01d1bbff8b8.webm?t=1576745789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/0fee023fc7644584482aa01d1bbff8b8.mp4?t=1576745789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Chill in Town</strong><br>Discover towns and other locales through your journey.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/5b667910f67e28ce00c8e97c4c7a5e2c.poster.avif?t=1576745789\" width=626 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/5b667910f67e28ce00c8e97c4c7a5e2c.webm?t=1576745789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145000/extras/5b667910f67e28ce00c8e97c4c7a5e2c.mp4?t=1576745789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
